## Step 1 - The atlas itself

Starting material should be as good quality as possible. I used `.eps` from [Paxinos Rat Atlas]() for doing this. On the cheap side, a *very* nice online resource can be found [here](http://labs.gaidi.ca/rat-brain-atlas/). Images could be imported to most image processing freeware. 

